data.title: 1989 Topps Batman Movie #93 The Joker Is Wild - NM-MT - The Dugout Sportscards & Comics
data.meta_description: 1989 Topps Batman Movie #93 The Joker Is Wild - The Dugout Sportscards & Comics - Check out your favorite player cards listed in Beckett Marketplace.
data.text:
Produced by Topps. Based on the movie of the same name, these cards’ fronts feature a photo image from the film, and the backs, with story text. In the first series, card fronts are surrounded by a white border, while cards in the second series have yellow borders. Both series alike, the sticker inserts have puzzle backs and make up two 10-card puzzle images, plus two finished images of what the puzzles look like. The first base set of cards are numbered 1 through 132, with sticker inserts numbered 1 through 22. And in every collector’s edition factory boxed set, 11 bonus cards numbered A through K featuring production art are added. The second base set continues from 133 through 264, the sticker inserts from 23 through 44, and as for every boxed set, bonus cards continue the numbering from L through V as well. Read Less »
